<BaseLayout title="Sign in — Janaushdhi" description="Janaushdhi is fully usable without an account.">
  <div class="page prose">
    <span class="pill">Account</span>
    <h1 style="margin-top:12px;">Sign in</h1>
    <p>Janaushdhi is fully usable <strong>without an account</strong>. You don't need to sign in to browse the catalogue, search medicines, or view prices.</p>
    <p>Optional account features (saved medicines, price-drop alerts) are on the roadmap but not live in v0. Want them sooner? <a href="/contact/">Let us know</a>.</p>
    <p style="margin-top:32px;"><a class="btn btn-primary" href="/browse/">Browse without an account →</a></p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
